                    <p class="t-shirt__container__info__body"><strong>Secundario: </strong>Rojo</p>
                    <hr>
                    <h4 class="t-shirt__container__info__title">Diseño</h4>
                    <p class="t-shirt__container__info__body"><strong>Patrón: </strong>Manchas</p>
                    <p class="t-shirt__container__info__body"><strong>Tipo de tela: </strong>Franela</p>
                    <p class="t-shirt__container__info__body"><strong>Manga larga: </strong>Si</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container__button">
            <a href="/group-recommendation"><button class="t-shirt__button">Descrubre la camisa de grupo</button></a>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <div class="container entry__container">
            <div class="entry__container__info">
