                                    </strong>{{pattern}}</p>
                                <p class="card-text card__container__t-shirt__wrap__info__body"><strong>Tipo de tela:
                                    </strong>{{material}}</p>
                                <p class="card-text card__container__t-shirt__wrap__info__body"><strong>Manga larga:
                                    </strong>{{long_sleeve}}</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
